name: MORNING TAKEOFFS from Calgary International Airport [4K]
description:
A clear morning in Calgary is one of the ultimate times to go plane spotting at YYC, with some unbeatable views of downtown and the Rockies in the distance!

This morning filmed back in April was a bit on the hazy side, but still had some great traffic and awesome city views. Enjoy these 19 departures!
